" data-medium-file="https://p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/chart_minus_image.png" data-large-file="https://p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/chart_minus_image.png" src="https://p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/chart_minus_image.png" alt="数据/聚合（负）" class="wp-image-115497"/></figure><p></p><p> ANYCOLOR 于 2 月 5 日宣布，由于“ <em><a href="https://p2y.jp/anycolor-terminates-nijisanji-en-new-vtuber-selen-tatsuki-due-to-repeated-contract-violations-and-misrepresentations-on-sns/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">多次违反合同以及在 SNS 上进行误导性和虚假的陈述和行为</a></em>”，它已终止与 Seren Ryugetsu 的合同。此外，该公司还受到海外VTuber观众和粉丝的激烈批评，其中<a href="https://p2y.jp/anycolor-announced-minor-financial-impact-from-nijisanji-en-new-selen-tatsuki-terminated/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">IR公告称<em>“对业绩的影响极小</em>”。</a></p><p> 2 月 13 日 Elira Pendora 频道播出以及 ANYCOLOR 社长<strong>卓野陆先生</strong>发表声明视频后，《NIJISANJI EN》（新）订阅人数进一步加速下滑。尽管自2月19日以来，部分人才开始呈现小幅复苏趋势，但势头极其微弱，远远无法弥补破纪录的跌幅。 </p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-jp wp-block-embed-p-2-y-jp"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="Mk8O66RDdJ"> <a href="https://p2y.jp/anycolors-ceo-tazumi-riku-released-statement-in-response-to-furious-criticism-of-the-company/">ANYCOLOR 总裁卓野陆 (Riku Takuno) 发表声明，回应对该公司的激烈批评。</a> </blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="“ANYCOLOR 总裁 Riku Takuno 发表声明，回应对该公司的激烈批评” — P2y.jp" src="https://p2y.jp/anycolors-ceo-tazumi-riku-released-statement-in-response-to-furious-criticism-of-the-company/embed/#?secret=xviQu9lb2V#?secret=Mk8O66RDdJ" data-secret="Mk8O66RDdJ" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figure><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-jp wp-block-embed-p-2-y-jp"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="psZCVjW2Bl"> <a href="https://p2y.jp/nijisanji-en-new-vtuber-elira-pendora-expressed-criticized-selen-tatsuki-and-support-for-anycolor/">NIJISANJI EN（新）VTuber Elira Pendora批评Seren Ryugetsu并表示支持ANYCOLOR</a> </blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="“NIJISANJI EN（新）VTuber Elira Pendora批评Seren Ryugetsu并表示支持ANYCOLOR” — P2y.jp" src="https://p2y.jp/nijisanji-en-new-vtuber-elira-pendora-expressed-criticized-selen-tatsuki-and-support-for-anycolor/embed/#?secret=Lkjb5GqQ6B#?secret=psZCVjW2Bl" data-secret="psZCVjW2Bl" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figure><p></p><p>另一方面，据称是Seren Ryugetsu的表演者/声音模特的VTuber <strong>Dokibird</strong>的订阅人数自2月5日以来迅速增加。虽然目前步伐放缓，但稳定增长仍在继续，截至2月29日7:00，人数已达到约64.2万人。 </p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-jp wp-block-embed-p-2-y-jp"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="2S5UdewUVW"> <a href="https://p2y.jp/vtuber-dokibird-reported-youtube-silver-creator-award-my-first-youtube-play-button-that-i-own/">VTuber Dokibird YouTube报道“Silver Shield”的到来“我拥有的第一个播放按钮”</a> </blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="“VTuber Dokibird YouTube 宣布“Silver Shield”到来 “我拥有的第一个播放按钮” — P2y.jp" src="https://p2y.jp/vtuber-dokibird-reported-youtube-silver-creator-award-my-first-youtube-play-button-that-i-own/embed/#?secret=KKViBnJzYw#?secret=2S5UdewUVW" data-secret="2S5UdewUVW" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figure><p></p><p>近期NIJISANJI EN（新）频道订阅人数“暴跌”，对ANYCOLOR的<strong>NIJISANJI项目</strong>整体影响极其巨大，截至2月4日（4周）订阅人数<strong>有所下降</strong>。记录<strong>人数为2,118,000人</strong>。</p><p></p><h3 id="outline__1" class="wp-block-heading" id="outline__1"> Nijisanji Project 订阅人数变化</h3><figure class="wp-block-table is-style-stripes"><table><tbody><tr><td><strong>汇总发布日期</strong></td